    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>潜入意识之海，解决怪奇事件吧</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一位“潜意者”。你需要运用这种实验性的技术，潜入一位叫“莉娜”的女性的意识之海中，对其记忆进行修复，进而解决一个离奇的失踪案。莉娜的潜意识里隐藏着众多的秘密。将它们全部找出来，以解明事件的真相吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/142e9821e830de5afab6b040f30cfebc.poster.avif?t=1769612171\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/142e9821e830de5afab6b040f30cfebc.webm?t=1769612171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/142e9821e830de5afab6b040f30cfebc.mp4?t=1769612171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>修复破损的记忆，解明遗失的过去</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你所调查的记忆都缺失了关键的部分。找出能够填补这些部分的东西，对记忆进行修复。遗失的记忆渐渐明朗，尘封的过去也将浮出水面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/0127edb84c8b8aa01a66122999c885c1.poster.avif?t=1769612171\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/0127edb84c8b8aa01a66122999c885c1.webm?t=1769612171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/0127edb84c8b8aa01a66122999c885c1.mp4?t=1769612171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>困难的同时颇具成就感的推理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正确答案从来都是合理的。然而却无法轻易发现。想要修复记忆，线索是不可或缺的。你需要偷听人们的私密对话，调查清楚每一个角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细推查记忆，找出正确的关联吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/435364480db93c126ff46e2feec8420c.poster.avif?t=1769612171\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/435364480db93c126ff46e2feec8420c.webm?t=1769612171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/435364480db93c126ff46e2feec8420c.mp4?t=1769612171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>悲痛的爱之物语</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本来深深相爱，却因某种理由而支离破碎的一对恋人。莉娜失去了记忆，塞巴斯蒂安则下落不明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场诡异的派对究竟隐藏了怎样的真相？埋藏在莉娜意识深处“后悔”那一部分中的悲剧又究竟是什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/ea019a67a8057965ad724b99f902a281.poster.avif?t=1769612171\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/ea019a67a8057965ad724b99f902a281.webm?t=1769612171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/ea019a67a8057965ad724b99f902a281.mp4?t=1769612171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>夺人眼球的游戏设计</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全文配音</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 运用了3D扫描技术，颇具特色的画面</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 荣获大奖的故事和谜题设计</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >约4-5小时的紧凑游戏流程 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开发团队 Indoor Sunglasses 的寄语</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259330/extras/1a76842433bcfac2db9c8e75dfd8ebeb.avif?t=1769612171\" width=600 height=196 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们虽然是一个小型的团队，但大家都拥有旺盛的好奇心，无不热衷于悬疑推理以及新的发现。在室内也要戴墨镜，是为了不让别人看到自己的泪水。我们的开发理念就是让玩家们自己意识到问题所在，并逐渐解决一个一开始自己都没有信心破解的难题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的成员是在制作早期学生时代版本的《潜意者》时相识，以自己失恋和离别的经验打造了那款游戏。而那款作品也获得了IGF 2023最佳学生作品奖的提名。在那之后，我们坚定了想让大家感到“自己比想象中更聪明”、“自己并非孤身一人”的理念，开始创作这款更加宏大的《潜意者》。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希望未来我们能给大家带来更多神秘且充满谜团的游戏。</p>",
